00:16:53.660 --> 00:16:57.680
It's a circular process,
let go; define; become.

00:16:57.680 --> 00:16:59.690
It's one that you repeat
over and over again.

00:16:59.690 --> 00:17:01.290
And it's really
an open framework.

00:17:01.290 --> 00:17:06.150
If software had an analogy,
this is an open source platform.

00:17:06.150 --> 00:17:07.950
What we really
felt was important

00:17:07.950 --> 00:17:11.890
