00:18:09.300 --> 00:18:13.990
And a key part of that is this
idea of shedding the noise.

00:18:13.990 --> 00:18:16.850
The noise as we define
it is everything

00:18:16.850 --> 00:18:19.440
that comes at you in
a way that doesn't

00:18:19.440 --> 00:18:21.640
take your own individual
identity into account.

00:18:21.640 --> 00:18:24.142
It's that inauthentic
you should be a lawyer,

00:18:24.142 --> 00:18:26.100
you should be a doctor,
you're not smart enough

00:18:26.100 --> 00:18:28.150
to be a doctor, you could
never go to college,

00:18:28.150 --> 00:18:29.270
you have to go to college.

00:18:29.270 --> 00:18:31.130
It's all of these
different elements

00:18:31.130 --> 00:18:33.851
that we're always
inundated from.

00:18:33.851 --> 00:18:35.350
And they can come
from our families.

00:18:35.350 --> 00:18:36.440
